<ref>{{cite news|title = 2014年中華民國地方公職人員選舉|url = https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2014%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89|accessdate = 2015-07-21|date = 2012-01-26|work = 維基百科|archive-date = 2020-08-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200810000050/https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2014%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89|dead-url = no}}</ref>
，相關候選人亦針對議題做出回應
<ref>{{cite news|author=張文馨|title=連柯競提都更 巢運都不滿意|url=http://www.storm.mg/article/36237|accessdate=2015-07-21|newspaper=[[風傳媒|風傳媒]]|date=2014-09-25|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924110748/http://www.storm.mg/article/36237|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月4日，巢運團體於[[台北市|台北市]][[仁愛路|仁愛路]]三段（[[宏盛帝寶|宏盛帝寶]]所在地，普遍被認為是台灣地價最高的[[豪宅|豪宅]]、住宅區）舉辦「夜宿仁愛路」活動<ref name=":4" >{{cite news|author=陳怡臻、沈婉玉、江碩涵|title=巢運遊行2萬人 夜宿帝寶…人不多|url=http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS1/8979010.shtml|accessdate=2014-10-05|newspaper=[[聯合報|聯合報]]|date=2014-10-05|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007052402/http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS1/8979010.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=孫窮理|title=夜宿仁愛路 攻擊發起線  降房價 巢運聲言緊盯修法|url=http://www.coolloud.org.tw/node/80319|accessdate=2014-10-07|newspaper=[[苦勞網|苦勞網]]|date=2014-10-05|archive-date=2020-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626035156/https://www.coolloud.org.tw/node/80319|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=徐義平、郭安家、盧姮倩|title=巢運夜宿 近2萬人躺帝寶前|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/819016|accessdate=2014-10-07|newspaper=自由時報|date=2014-10-05|archive-date=2018-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209203941/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/819016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

